@SpringBootTest @AutoConfigureMockMvc public abstract class AdminEndpointTest<T,I extends Serializable,R extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<T,I>> extends TestFunctionProvider<T,I,R>
Abstract class to help with testing the integration of endpoints. This class provides some basic tests to test functionality with admin access level.
